\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\rtlch\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\fs24\lang1033\loch\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 \tab One particular day I boarded the bus wearing a bright blue Hawaiian print shirt - these were the trendiest thing imaginable and I was wearing one at exactly the right time, not a few months late like usual.  I had science class first period and I could no
