\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\rtlch\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\fs24\lang1033\loch\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 \tab \'93You look like one of those dead animals in a jar\'94 someone said, my face pressed painfully into the chainlink wall as I attempted to push the door open by force.  I was getting close.  I was nervous but laughing a little, and so were the guys, and in the 
